claim.claim-text:
Server apparatus (106), comprising;

a cache (212) operable to store a plurality of copies of transcoded media content, each of said plurality of copies having a different destination type;

a web-server interface (202) operable to receive a request from a user terminal for sending one of the plurality of copies of transcoded media content, wherein the user terminal indicates a URL designating one of the plurality of copies of transcoded media content to send to the user terminal; and

a streaming server (222) operable to transmit the transcoded media content indicated according to the URL to the user terminal.
